caption.title: Neighbor-joining phylogenetic tree of HAdV-7 sequences based on penton base (a), hexon (b), and fiber genes (c).
caption.p: The red circles indicate the HAdV-7 strains identified in this study; blue triangles indicate the HAdV-7 strains isolated in China from GenBank database; underlined strains are known types of HAdV-7 identified by REA; green diamonds indicate other members within species B.
